00:04:00.260 --> 00:04:01.260
Huntington, Mendebaldeko Virginia.

00:04:01.260 --> 00:04:03.260
Herri polita.

00:04:03.260 --> 00:04:06.260
Bertan utzi nuen nire arima, bihotza eta jendea,

00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:08.260
zuen jendea,

00:04:08.260 --> 00:04:10.260
